cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): This paper is about analyzing end-to-end speech recognition systems, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and speech processing. 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper deals with speech synthesis and speech enhancement, which are related to sound processing. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses deep neural networks for end-to-end speech recognition, which is a machine learning technique. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses AI techniques for speech recognition and analysis. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): Although not directly related, some of the techniques used in computer vision, such as convolutional neural networks, are also used in speech recognition, so this category is also a possibility.
